    "description": "We at Aptech Advisory Limited are looking for an experienced Teacher based out of Ranchi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Aptech Advisory Limited:\nAptech Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aptech Advisory Limited!",
